items.consumable

Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • items.Item
      • items.consumable.Food
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Food
extends Item
    This class represents food. A food type item makes the player heal when used. These type of items have a cook state. For more info., see CookState.
    See Also:

      • use

        public int use()
        This method makes use of a food type item. When used, the player heals the amount of HP specified in the food's heal value field. Food can only be used if their cook state is cooked. For more info., see CookState.
        Specified by:
        use in class Item
        Returns:
        1 if the food could be eaten, or 0 if not.
